The Mailbox.py code is dependent upon the pushbullet.py software package.
To install this on Unix Systems type the following:

  sudo pip install pushbullet.py

This will install pushbullet and all its dependencies to:
  /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages

The documentation for how to use the pushbullet dist is located at:
  github.com/randomchars/pushbullet.py

The sensor module is dependent upon the use of an analog converter. 
To install functionality onto the Raspberry Pi, follow the SPI instructions on the following url:
  http://www.instructables.com/id/Wiring-up-a-MCP3008-ADC-to-a-Raspberry-Pi-model-B-/?ALLSTEPS


